sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / Gateway<br/>(EPP sets headers)
    participant Sidecar as Routing Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS
    participant SSRF as SSRF Validator<br/>(in-process)
    participant Prefiller as Remote Prefiller vLLM<br/>Variable Port HTTP(S)
    participant Decoder as Local Decoder vLLM<br/>8001/TCP HTTP(S)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over K8sAPI,SSRF: Flow 3: SSRF Allowlist Updates (background)
    K8sAPI-->>SSRF: Watch InferencePool + Pods<br/>(informer list+watch, 30s resync)
    SSRF-->>SSRF: Rebuild pod IP/name allowlist

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 1: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (NIXL v2)
    Client->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Header: x-prefiller-host-port<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Sidecar->>SSRF: Validate prefiller host<br/>against InferencePool allowlist
    SSRF-->>Sidecar: Allowed (or HTTP 403)
    Sidecar->>Sidecar: Generate UUID (x-request-id)
    Sidecar->>Prefiller: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>stream=false, max_tokens=1<br/>kv_transfer_params: {do_remote_decode: true}
    Prefiller-->>Sidecar: Response with kv_transfer_params<br/>(block_ids, engine_id, host, port)
    Sidecar->>Decoder: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Original stream/max_tokens restored<br/>kv_transfer_params from prefiller attached
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Streaming response (tokens)
    Sidecar-->>Client: Streaming response<br/>TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 2: Passthrough (No Disaggregation)
    Client->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(no x-prefiller-host-port)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Sidecar->>Decoder: Direct proxy forward<br/>HTTP(S)/8001
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Response
    Sidecar-->>Client: Response<br/>TLS 1.2+
